<div class="section    " id="skills" style="padding-top:20px; padding-bottom:40px; background-color:" ><div class="section_wrapper clearfix"><div class="items_group clearfix"><div class="column one column_fancy_heading"><div class="fancy_heading fancy_heading_line"><h2 class="title">Mission Statement</h2><div class="inside"><div style="
    text-align: left;
    color: #626262;
">
The Drake Foundation was set up as a means to improve measures for participant safety in all contact sports. Our dedicated team has a deeply rooted love of sport and is passionate about the safety of all its participants, ensuring research is continued, and safety improved for years to come.
</div>
