</div><div class="column one column_column"><div class="column_attr  align_center" ><span class="mission-statement-subtitle">Our objectives are:</span></div></div><div class="column one-second column_column"><div class="column_attr " ><span class="mission-statement-column">i) To carry out dedicated research and investigations into sports-related concussion and its short- and long-term effects, with an ultimate goal of improving measures for participant safety in all contact sports.</span></div></div><div class="column one-second column_column"><div class="column_attr " ><span class="mission-statement-column">ii) To sponsor, organise, carry out or be involved in any investigation, research, educational programme or other activity, which is directly or indirectly connected with concussion, head injuries or sport-related illness or injury.</span>
</div></div></div></div></div>